reviewText:
Excellent movie about what was going on in Minnesota's history concerning how St. Paul became an Oasis for the hoodlum's of the times.  See what happen when Ma Barker, and her sons along with Alvin Karpis, and John Dillinger met up with the new police commissioner.

Also, if you love vintage cars, this movie is a must see for you. A lot of collector's rolling eye candy to appreciate.
